headline: Is the Schwab US Dividend Equity ETF a Buy Now?
summary: The Schwab US Dividend Equity ETF is dividend-focused, but it comes with an important twist.  The Schwab US Dividend Equity ETF has a solid history of capital and dividend growth.  The Schwab US Dividend Equity ETF (NYSEMKT: SCHD) has around $68 billion in assets, which suggests it is a very popular exchange-traded fund (ETF).
